@@TJvDockDelphiZone
Summary
  A docking zone implementation.
Description
  TJvDockDelphiZone is used by the TJvDockDelphiStyle to define the behavior for dock zones when using
  Delphi style docking.
  
  You do not need to create this component yourself. It is handled automatically by the
  TJvDockDelphiStyle component.

