@@TJvDockDelphiStyle
<TITLEIMG TJvDockDelphiStyle>
#JVCLInfo
<GROUP JVCL.Docking>
<FLAG Component>
Summary
  Defines standard Delphi docking behavior.
Description
  Drop a TJvDockDelphiStyle on a form when you want the form to dock in the same way as standard
  Delphi. To activate the docking, drop a TJvDockServer or TJvDockClient on the same form and set its
  DockStyle property to point to the TJvDockDelphiStyle component.

